1
00:00:05,696 --> 00:00:08,392
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,465 --> 00:00:12,333
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,403 --> 00:00:16,396
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,740 --> 00:00:19,231
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,310 --> 00:00:23,371
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,447 --> 00:00:27,406
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,886 --> 00:00:33,619
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,325 --> 00:00:37,294
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:41,823
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,566 --> 00:00:43,863
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,201 --> 00:00:46,761
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,812 --> 00:01:00,182
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,384 --> 00:01:01,544
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,618 --> 00:01:05,418
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,756 --> 00:01:10,955
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,228 --> 00:01:12,559
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,629 --> 00:01:14,028
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,098 --> 00:01:20,367
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:36,141 --> 00:01:38,735
Ugh... what are you here for now?

20
00:01:39,044 --> 00:01:43,310
It's our reunion after so long,
and you're awfully cold.

21
00:01:44,549 --> 00:01:47,916
Don't tell me that you came to
assassinate Lord Hokage?

22
00:01:48,186 --> 00:01:49,619
No, no...

23
00:01:50,188 --> 00:01:52,713
I don't have enough
subordinates for that yet...

24
00:01:52,957 --> 00:01:55,619
I've heard of the excellence ones
of this village

25
00:01:55,694 --> 00:01:57,355
and thought I'd put dibs on them.

26
00:02:02,634 --> 00:02:07,469
A little while ago, I gave that
same Curse Mark as a present.

27
00:02:09,207 --> 00:02:10,799
There's a kid that I want.

28
00:02:12,444 --> 00:02:13,968
Selfish as always.

29
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:16,037
That kid will die.

30
00:02:17,015 --> 00:02:17,777
Certainly...

31
00:02:18,149 --> 00:02:20,777
The odds are 1 in 10
that he'll survive,

32
00:02:21,286 --> 00:02:24,915
but he may survive just like you did.

33
00:02:25,957 --> 00:02:28,482
This kid, you really like him, huh?

34
00:02:29,961 --> 00:02:31,360
Are you jealous?

35
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:37,991
Are you still holding a grudge that
I used you and threw you away?

36
00:02:40,672 --> 00:02:43,766
Unlike you, that kid will excel...

37
00:02:44,242 --> 00:02:48,042
For one thing, he inherited
the Uchiha ability.

38
00:02:49,948 --> 00:02:51,711
He has beautiful features

39
00:02:51,783 --> 00:02:54,513
and is a vessel who
can become my heir.

40
00:02:55,019 --> 00:02:58,921
If that kid lived,
it makes things interesting.

41
00:02:59,457 --> 00:03:03,154
Be sure not to cancel this test.

42
00:03:05,063 --> 00:03:08,362
Three from my village are also
under your care...

43
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,734
Make me enjoy it.

44
00:03:13,538 --> 00:03:17,531
If something happens
to deprive me of my fun,

45
00:03:18,243 --> 00:03:21,269
consider it the end of Leaf Village

46
00:03:39,631 --> 00:03:42,600
We've secured food and water
after spending half a day.

47
00:03:43,201 --> 00:03:46,170
And now most teams have halted activity.

48
00:03:47,806 --> 00:03:50,138
As we planned,
this is the time that we attack.

49
00:03:50,642 --> 00:03:53,202
We'll split up into three
and go scouting.

50
00:03:53,545 --> 00:03:56,810
However, whether we find
other teams or not,

51
00:03:57,415 --> 00:03:59,406
we return to this place.

52
00:04:00,952 --> 00:04:01,680
Got it?

53
00:04:02,253 --> 00:04:03,049
Okay.

54
00:04:03,221 --> 00:04:04,017
Roger.

55
00:04:05,023 --> 00:04:06,684
Okay. Scatter!

56
00:04:12,997 --> 00:04:17,900
<i>Bushy Brow's Pledge.</i>
<i>Undying Love and Protection!</i>

57
00:05:11,723 --> 00:05:13,623
<i>I can't fall asleep...</i>

58
00:05:16,127 --> 00:05:18,595
<i>I need to protect these two.</i>

59
00:05:30,241 --> 00:05:32,038
I slept great!

60
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:33,168
Naruto!

61
00:05:35,613 --> 00:05:36,705
Sasuke!

62
00:05:36,948 --> 00:05:39,212
Did you take care of us?

63
00:05:39,584 --> 00:05:41,176
Thank you, Sakura!

64
00:05:41,252 --> 00:05:43,413
We're totally better because of you!

65
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:46,814
That's good...

66
00:05:51,863 --> 00:05:57,768
A prey must always stay tense
and flee desperately

67
00:05:58,670 --> 00:06:00,695
in front of the predator!

68
00:06:11,583 --> 00:06:12,572
<i>My voice is gone!</i>

69
00:06:25,229 --> 00:06:26,890
<i>It was just a dream...</i>

70
00:06:32,837 --> 00:06:34,134
<i>Is it daybreak already?!</i>

71
00:06:36,641 --> 00:06:37,505
<i>No, no way!</i>

72
00:06:52,624 --> 00:06:53,522
A squirrel?

73
00:06:54,025 --> 00:06:56,926
Don't surprise me like that!

74
00:06:57,362 --> 00:06:58,158
Oh!

75
00:07:02,066 --> 00:07:03,397
<i>That was too close.</i>

76
00:07:04,302 --> 00:07:05,667
Do you think she noticed?

77
00:07:06,037 --> 00:07:08,062
The Paper Bomb we put on the squirrel...

78
00:07:08,339 --> 00:07:10,307
No, that's not it.

79
00:07:10,642 --> 00:07:14,100
Huh? Then what? What was it?

80
00:07:14,412 --> 00:07:16,903
We'll probably find out if we go closer.

81
00:07:18,249 --> 00:07:21,446
So... we should get going now.

82
00:07:40,772 --> 00:07:44,572
<i>If I can catch all twenty of these leaves</i>
<i>before they hit the ground</i>

83
00:07:44,642 --> 00:07:47,839
<i>Sakura will start to like me.</i>

84
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:51,373
<i>Lf...if I can't catch</i>
<i>even one of the leaves...!</i>

85
00:07:52,016 --> 00:07:55,417
<i>Lt'll be an unanswered love forever.</i>
<i>Or rather...</i>

86
00:07:55,486 --> 00:07:56,851
You're too Bushy!

87
00:07:57,388 --> 00:07:58,719
<i>That's what she'll say.</i>

88
00:08:01,926 --> 00:08:03,655
One, two, three, four...
five, six, seven, eight...

89
00:08:03,728 --> 00:08:06,094
nine, ten, eleven, twelve, thirteen, fourteen,
fifteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen,

90
00:08:06,164 --> 00:08:09,930
nine!
Ugh, nineteen...

91
00:08:11,135 --> 00:08:12,124
One more!

92
00:08:15,707 --> 00:08:16,401
That's...!

93
00:08:23,514 --> 00:08:25,311
Phew... just in time.

94
00:08:26,984 --> 00:08:30,476
This is called a Paper Bomb
and it explodes after some time.

95
00:08:31,723 --> 00:08:33,623
Who did such an awful thing?

96
00:08:41,599 --> 00:08:43,362
Stop hiding and come out.

97
00:08:44,535 --> 00:08:47,163
Shoot! We scrambled to hide, you know?!

98
00:08:47,772 --> 00:08:51,367
Man, he's a damn pain
and we've been discovered!

99
00:08:51,809 --> 00:08:55,438
Strategy One, "hide and let it pass,"
was a failure!

100
00:08:55,813 --> 00:08:58,475
So now we carry out Strategy Two!

101
00:08:58,549 --> 00:09:01,416
Huh? Are you serious?

102
00:09:01,652 --> 00:09:04,052
What? You have a problem with that?

103
00:09:04,388 --> 00:09:06,379
There's no question of success.

104
00:09:07,024 --> 00:09:09,322
Well, I guess it's all right but...

105
00:09:10,495 --> 00:09:16,695
Wow! To meet last year's Number One
rookie, Neji Hyuga, in a place like this!

106
00:09:16,768 --> 00:09:19,202
C-Can I have your autograph?

107
00:09:19,370 --> 00:09:21,099
So it's just you guys?

108
00:09:21,572 --> 00:09:25,872
<i>Take that! Strategy Two, "head over heals</i>
<i>infatuation with my sex appeal"!</i>

109
00:09:26,611 --> 00:09:32,350
I'd been wanting to meet you
for some time, you know?

110
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:33,112
Get lost!

111
00:09:36,154 --> 00:09:39,590
<i>Why? Why doesn't my sexiness work?!</i>

112
00:09:39,657 --> 00:09:43,354
<i>Shoot, it ticks me off, damn!</i>

113
00:09:45,663 --> 00:09:50,191
Did you just raise your fists to me,
and does that mean you want to fight?

114
00:09:50,368 --> 00:09:54,930
N-No...
Of course not.

115
00:09:55,673 --> 00:09:56,765
Then get lost.

116
00:09:57,341 --> 00:10:00,708
Stealing a scroll from cowardly wimps
like you

117
00:10:00,778 --> 00:10:03,110
would only make me
the laughing stock of the village

118
00:10:03,247 --> 00:10:04,976
Y-Yes!

119
00:10:06,083 --> 00:10:08,847
Huh... Really just like cockroaches.

120
00:10:14,592 --> 00:10:16,457
<i>Just as I thought.</i>

121
00:10:16,527 --> 00:10:21,089
<i>A fellow like that wouldn't take</i>
<i>a scroll away from wimps like us</i>

122
00:10:21,165 --> 00:10:23,326
<i>unless we were to turn on him.</i>

123
00:10:23,401 --> 00:10:26,598
All right! Let's go find some wimps!

124
00:10:27,905 --> 00:10:31,272
<i>Like I've been saying</i>
<i>there's no one wimpier than us...</i>

125
00:10:43,387 --> 00:10:45,355
So a no sleep lookout?

126
00:10:47,124 --> 00:10:49,058
But it's not necessary anymore.

127
00:10:49,861 --> 00:10:55,026
Wake Sasuke up.
We want to battle with him.

128
00:10:55,633 --> 00:10:57,157
<i>Y-You bastards...</i>

129
00:11:00,371 --> 00:11:01,633
What're you saying?

130
00:11:01,706 --> 00:11:03,537
What is it you're after?

131
00:11:03,741 --> 00:11:06,733
I know the one called Orochimaru
is calling the shots from the shadows!

132
00:11:07,144 --> 00:11:07,940
Huh?!

133
00:11:08,646 --> 00:11:11,080
What's that strange bruise on
the back of Sasuke's neck?

134
00:11:12,149 --> 00:11:13,912
You did this to Sasuke.

135
00:11:13,985 --> 00:11:15,475
How can you say you want to fight him?!

136
00:11:16,487 --> 00:11:21,049
I wonder... what he has on his mind?

137
00:11:23,194 --> 00:11:26,322
However, I can't stay quiet
after hearing that.

138
00:11:27,131 --> 00:11:31,124
I will kill this girl,
I'll also kill this Sasuke character.

139
00:11:36,007 --> 00:11:37,304
Wait, Zaku.

140
00:11:37,575 --> 00:11:38,940
Huh? What is it?

141
00:11:42,546 --> 00:11:44,104
It's so cliché.

142
00:11:44,782 --> 00:11:47,649
It's the color of dirt
that's just been dug up.

143
00:11:47,952 --> 00:11:51,012
This grass, it doesn't grow in
a place like this, does it?

144
00:11:51,289 --> 00:11:52,085
<i>Damn!</i>

145
00:11:52,890 --> 00:11:54,653
You know, with a trap...

146
00:11:55,026 --> 00:11:58,120
there's no point unless you
make it so it's not discovered.

147
00:11:59,916 --> 00:12:01,850
Huh, how ridiculous!

148
00:12:02,152 --> 00:12:06,589
So that Kunai knife was so the squirrel
wouldn't be caught in the trap?

149
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:08,484
We kill her now!

150
00:12:12,829 --> 00:12:13,523
A log?!

151
00:12:13,930 --> 00:12:15,955
A trap above too? Watch out!

152
00:12:17,067 --> 00:12:18,500
Just kidding.

153
00:12:20,737 --> 00:12:21,635
What?!

154
00:12:21,972 --> 00:12:24,440
Clearly you have no talent.

155
00:12:25,175 --> 00:12:28,872
Someone like you needs to
make more of an effort or else!

156
00:12:30,313 --> 00:12:31,439
Leaf Hurricanes!

157
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:39,750
What?! This guy...

158
00:12:40,624 --> 00:12:43,923
Then you also should... make an effort!

159
00:12:45,028 --> 00:12:46,154
Who are you?

160
00:12:46,463 --> 00:12:50,126
I'm the beautiful blue beast
of Leaf Village, Rock Lee!

161
00:13:04,881 --> 00:13:06,678
Why are you here?

162
00:13:06,883 --> 00:13:08,111
I will always appear...

163
00:13:08,752 --> 00:13:12,017
whenever you're in trouble!

164
00:13:14,691 --> 00:13:15,783
Or should I say...

165
00:13:15,859 --> 00:13:19,420
It was really because of you,
now run along.

166
00:13:26,036 --> 00:13:29,699
But right now, I'm also
your enemy!

167
00:13:30,307 --> 00:13:32,070
I did say this once before, didn't I?

168
00:13:34,511 --> 00:13:36,342
That I'll protect you until I die.

169
00:13:39,783 --> 00:13:41,410
<i>Please go out with me!</i>

170
00:13:41,751 --> 00:13:43,981
I'll protect you until I die!

171
00:13:46,056 --> 00:13:46,852
Oh...

172
00:13:47,824 --> 00:13:49,485
T-Thanks.

173
00:13:50,126 --> 00:13:50,820
Yes!

174
00:13:50,894 --> 00:13:54,557
Perfect! I did it!
Guy Sensei, that was perfect!

175
00:13:57,901 --> 00:13:59,630
I guess it can't be helped...

176
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:03,403
Zaku. I'll give you Sasuke.

177
00:14:05,108 --> 00:14:06,803
I will kill them!

178
00:14:08,244 --> 00:14:11,543
<i>As far as I can tell,</i>
<i>Sakura is in no condition to fight.</i>

179
00:14:12,282 --> 00:14:15,979
<i>That Bushy Brow guy is</i>
<i>pretty proficient with Taijutsu...</i>

180
00:14:16,152 --> 00:14:18,177
<i>Looks like I can have some fun!</i>

181
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:30,997
There is a trick to your attack, isn't there?

182
00:14:31,568 --> 00:14:33,229
I won't just simply avoid it.

183
00:14:34,571 --> 00:14:36,937
You showed me your Jutsu before.

184
00:14:40,777 --> 00:14:42,836
<i>This guy...he's strong.</i>

185
00:14:43,246 --> 00:14:44,372
<i>Having said that,</i>

186
00:14:44,447 --> 00:14:46,244
<i>the odds aren't good since</i>
<i>it's one versus three.</i>

187
00:14:46,616 --> 00:14:48,174
<i>I'm gonna have to take a chance.</i>

188
00:14:51,988 --> 00:14:53,012
<i>One person at a time...</i>

189
00:14:53,089 --> 00:14:54,784
<i>I'll give it my all and take each down!</i>

190
00:15:05,201 --> 00:15:07,931
There's no one at all that seems wimpy!

191
00:15:08,505 --> 00:15:13,966
Well, the only team that's weaker
than us is the Naruto team.

192
00:15:14,043 --> 00:15:16,238
Idiot! You know what you're saying?

193
00:15:16,379 --> 00:15:17,038
What?!

194
00:15:17,113 --> 00:15:19,479
No question Naruto and Sakura are lame!

195
00:15:19,549 --> 00:15:22,347
But that team has
the super genius Sasuke!

196
00:15:22,585 --> 00:15:24,644
Hah! I wonder...

197
00:15:24,821 --> 00:15:28,655
In actual battle that genius
might easily be beaten.

198
00:15:28,858 --> 00:15:30,120
What?!

199
00:15:32,128 --> 00:15:35,063
All right, all right,
I apologize for irritating you.

200
00:15:35,999 --> 00:15:38,365
<i>What a pain...</i>

201
00:15:38,535 --> 00:15:43,438
<i>I say one negative thing about</i>
<i>Sasuke and I get the evil eye, every time...</i>

202
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:46,936
There's no way Sasuke
could be taken down!

203
00:15:47,844 --> 00:15:50,074
Sakura's a different matter though!

204
00:15:54,350 --> 00:15:55,749
Huh?!

205
00:15:56,719 --> 00:15:58,744
Hey! Sasuke has collapsed...

206
00:15:58,988 --> 00:15:59,545
Huh?!

207
00:15:59,622 --> 00:16:01,817
...and Sakura is fighting.

208
00:16:02,058 --> 00:16:03,150
What did you say?

209
00:16:08,498 --> 00:16:09,362
Hey!

210
00:16:11,801 --> 00:16:13,735
He's late.

211
00:16:13,937 --> 00:16:15,131
That Lee...

212
00:16:15,972 --> 00:16:17,200
Something's not right.

213
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:20,136
He's always precise about time.

214
00:16:21,311 --> 00:16:23,142
Perhaps he ran into the enemy...

215
00:16:24,914 --> 00:16:25,881
Could it be?

216
00:16:26,816 --> 00:16:29,250
Huh, that wouldn't have happened.

217
00:16:30,353 --> 00:16:32,548
In any case, let's find Lee!

218
00:16:32,989 --> 00:16:33,751
Right!

219
00:16:40,830 --> 00:16:44,266
Yes! I've finally mastered it!
Yes! Yes!

220
00:16:44,667 --> 00:16:48,535
My friends, there's no reason
to give up on your youth!

221
00:16:56,546 --> 00:16:57,638
<i>This Jutsu...</i>

222
00:16:57,814 --> 00:17:00,749
<i>In the end, only Lee</i>
<i>could make it his own.</i>

223
00:17:01,217 --> 00:17:02,149
Yahoo!

224
00:17:02,218 --> 00:17:04,618
- Hey Lee...
- I did it! I will do it!

225
00:17:04,687 --> 00:17:06,348
- Lee!
- When I try! I try!

226
00:17:06,422 --> 00:17:07,354
Hey, Lee!

227
00:17:09,592 --> 00:17:11,116
Hey!

228
00:17:15,765 --> 00:17:18,962
Listen to this passionate message
from your teacher!

229
00:17:19,035 --> 00:17:20,366
Oh... what is it?!

230
00:17:20,603 --> 00:17:22,730
Please tell me using hip words.

231
00:17:26,042 --> 00:17:27,634
This Jutsu, the "Lotus"...

232
00:17:27,977 --> 00:17:30,309
it will be dealt with henceforth
as a forbidden Jutsu.

233
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:31,945
- What?!
- Huh?!

234
00:17:33,182 --> 00:17:34,706
W-What do you mean?

235
00:17:35,552 --> 00:17:39,921
This Jutsu poses a great burden
on the cells of the muscles,

236
00:17:39,989 --> 00:17:42,423
it's a kind of "Self sacrificing Technique."

237
00:17:43,526 --> 00:17:47,485
Humans normally utilize,
at most, 20 percent...

238
00:17:47,564 --> 00:17:50,260
of the "power" that the muscles have.

239
00:17:50,366 --> 00:17:52,334
Do you understand?
Only 20 percent!

240
00:17:52,902 --> 00:17:55,393
And if nearly 100 percent
of the "power" is used

241
00:17:55,471 --> 00:17:57,803
the muscles themselves will disintegrate.

242
00:17:58,107 --> 00:18:02,339
So, the brain usually controls the "power."

243
00:18:03,246 --> 00:18:08,548
However, this Jutsu forces the
brain's limiter to go off by using Chakra,

244
00:18:08,618 --> 00:18:11,985
allowing high speed continuous Taijutsu...

245
00:18:12,522 --> 00:18:15,514
In other words, this is a dangerous Jutsu
which relies on a secret technique

246
00:18:15,592 --> 00:18:19,255
that brings forth "power" almost
to the limit of one's body.

247
00:18:21,564 --> 00:18:24,294
So the only time it is all right
to use this Jutsu

248
00:18:24,367 --> 00:18:26,426
is when a certain condition is met...

249
00:18:27,570 --> 00:18:29,970
So... when is that?

250
00:18:31,975 --> 00:18:32,771
Are you ready?

251
00:18:33,376 --> 00:18:34,843
Take this to heart...

252
00:18:35,945 --> 00:18:37,378
The condition is...

253
00:18:41,017 --> 00:18:42,609
<i>The condition is...</i>

254
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:48,522
<i>Guy Sensei...</i>

255
00:18:49,258 --> 00:18:52,421
<i>I will utilize that Jutsu without reserve.</i>

256
00:18:53,529 --> 00:18:55,554
<i>Because this is the time you said...</i>

257
00:18:59,836 --> 00:19:02,327
"When protecting a precious person!"

258
00:19:04,173 --> 00:19:05,003
<i>He disappeared?!</i>

259
00:19:09,912 --> 00:19:10,901
It's just the beginning.

260
00:19:19,288 --> 00:19:20,277
Oh, oh no!

261
00:19:20,523 --> 00:19:22,286
There's no way he can break his fall!

262
00:19:23,426 --> 00:19:25,018
Take this!

263
00:19:25,261 --> 00:19:26,694
Primary Lotus!

264
00:19:35,271 --> 00:19:36,329
<i>This feeling...</i>

265
00:19:38,975 --> 00:19:40,408
Well well...

266
00:19:43,146 --> 00:19:44,841
Just in time.

267
00:19:53,856 --> 00:19:54,948
T-That's impossible!

268
00:19:56,025 --> 00:19:58,118
That is a frightening Jutsu...

269
00:19:58,695 --> 00:20:02,324
It did this much even though
I fell on the spongy dirt.

270
00:20:06,502 --> 00:20:08,993
It's now my turn.

271
00:20:09,739 --> 00:20:11,900
<i>Oh no! With what I just did...</i>

272
00:20:12,341 --> 00:20:13,501
<i>my body still isn't...</i>

273
00:20:18,014 --> 00:20:18,776
Lee!

274
00:20:25,354 --> 00:20:28,323
Your Jutsu is indeed fast.

275
00:20:30,226 --> 00:20:34,890
But our Jutsu exceeds that
and is the speed of sound!

276
00:20:39,535 --> 00:20:43,869
I'll show you there are walls

277
00:20:44,140 --> 00:20:45,732
which effort alone can
never break through.

278
00:21:05,512 --> 00:21:10,108
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

279
00:21:10,217 --> 00:21:18,317
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

280
00:21:19,392 --> 00:21:27,925
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

281
00:21:28,535 --> 00:21:36,237
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

282
00:21:37,644 --> 00:21:43,173
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

283
00:21:43,250 --> 00:21:47,016
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

284
00:21:47,087 --> 00:21:50,648
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

285
00:21:51,124 --> 00:21:59,532
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

286
00:21:59,933 --> 00:22:04,996
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

287
00:22:05,071 --> 00:22:09,474
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

288
00:22:09,643 --> 00:22:13,306
<i>Just sing.</i>

289
00:22:13,613 --> 00:22:18,710
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

290
00:22:18,852 --> 00:22:20,979
<i>The two are one</i>

291
00:22:21,087 --> 00:22:27,356
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

292
00:22:27,961 --> 00:22:32,955
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

293
00:22:36,969 --> 00:22:40,496
I'm so frustrated!
I'm just pulling feet again.

294
00:22:40,906 --> 00:22:44,603
I'm always just being protected.
I always just watch them from behind.

295
00:22:45,378 --> 00:22:47,710
This time, I need to protect everyone!

296
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:50,273
Naruto, Sakuke, Lee!

297
00:22:50,683 --> 00:22:53,880
I want to be like you too!

298
00:22:54,854 --> 00:22:58,051
Next episode:
"Sakura Blossoms!"

299
00:22:58,624 --> 00:23:01,422
Please watch my battle...
